注释类型 Array


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Array
    Annotation that indicates that a field is an array type.

    • 必需元素概要

      所需元素 
      限定符和类型 必需的元素和说明
      Class component
      Component type.

    • 可选元素概要

      Whether components may be null.

      Maximum number of elements in the array. -1 means no maximum.
